-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                     FRAPPUCINO - Java Desktop Component Library
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
 Frappucino is a library containing useful swing components useful for desktop applications.

 For the latest information on new releases, website or ressource changes, 
 please visit http://columba.sourceforge.net


